rested-3458053">在她的眼睛上方缝了针</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3459626" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3459626" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3459626" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage.jpg" alt="贝比·雷克萨" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bebe-rexha-returns-to-stage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3459626" class="wp-caption-text"> Bebe Rexha 出席 2023 年 5 月 25 日在法国安提布海角伊登罗克角酒店举行的 amfAR 2023 年戛纳盛典（图片来源：Andreas Rentz/amfAR/Getty Images for amfAR）</figcaption></figure><p>此后，流行歌星警告粉丝不要在舞台上向他们扔东西， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/latto-says-someone-will-get-their-ass-beat-if-a-fan-threw-something-at-her-again-3469364-3469364">其中包括拉托</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-calls-on-fans-to-stop-throwing-things-at-artists-on-stage-3464740">阿黛尔</a>。</p><p>本月早些时候，德雷克在最近的芝加哥演出中被手机击中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fan-throws-phone-drake-during-tour-kickoff-chicago-its-all-a-blur-21-savage-3466160">，成为最新一位被扔东西的艺术家</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>还对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-fans-throwing-objects-at-performers-is-infuriating-3468291">粉丝向舞台上的艺术家投掷物品的趋势发表了看法，称其为“令人愤怒”</a> 。</p><p>上个月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-bunny">坏兔子</a>回忆起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bad-bunny-addresses-throwing-disrespectful-fans-phone-after-they-attempted-a-selfie-3459473">当粉丝试图在街上与他自拍时，他扔掉了一名粉丝的手机的</a>那一刻。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/whoopi-goldberg-walks-off-talkshow-during-heated-discussion-3470445">乌比·戈德堡在激烈讨论中退出脱口秀的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
