0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cluckin-bell-grand-theft-auto-real-life-version-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cluckin-bell-grand-theft-auto-real-life-version-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cluckin-bell-grand-theft-auto-real-life-version-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/cluckin-bell-grand-theft-auto-real-life-version-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/take-two-interactive">Take-Two Interactive</a>的法律代表向他们发送了一份停止函后，想要重建<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto"><em>《侠盗猎车手》</em></a>中的两家餐厅的团队正在改变其行动方针。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/grand-theft-auto-vice-city-80s-soundtrack-3231742">侠盗猎车手 – 罪恶都市 80 年代原声带 20 周年</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<em><a href="https://rockstarintel.com/company-behind-the-irl-burger-shot-cluckin-bell-restaurant-receives-cease-desist-by-take-two">Rockstar Intel</a></em>的报告，Smokin J&#39;s BBQ 和 Boyworldwide 正在本周在圣地亚哥动漫展上合作推出 Cluckin&#39; Bell and Burger Shot 快闪店。然而，Smokin J&#39;s BBQ 却不得不让<em>《侠盗猎车手》的</em>粉丝们稍感失望，因为 Take-Two Interactive 并未授予其对其知识产权的模仿许可。 </p><figure id="attachment_3470450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3470450" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3470450" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/burger-shot-gta-4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3470450" class="wp-caption-text"> 《侠盗猎车手 4》中的汉堡图片来源：Take-Two Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> “昨晚，我们收到了代表 Take-Two Interactive 的律师事务所发来的停止函。作为回应，我们被迫取消原定于本周末（动漫展）举行的 Burger Shot 活动，”发送给 Rockstar Intel 的有关该活动的电子邮件中写道。</p><p> “下周末我们仍将进行 Cluckin&#39; Bell 类型的装置，但现在它将是一个名为 Dont Cluckin Tell 的恶搞装置，”Smokin J 的 BBQ 说道。</p><p>这是 Smokin J&#39;s BBQ 和 Boyworldwide 第二次合作开展以<em>《侠盗猎车手》</em>为灵感的快闪项目。去年，两家公司成功宣传了一家 Cluckin&#39; Bell Chicken 餐厅，其中包括员工制服、菜单和比赛中的标牌。</p><p>由于最初的快闪店取得了巨大成功，因此团队希望扩大规模以提供 Burger Shot 是可以理解的。与此同时，Take-Two Interactive 很可能正在等待某种公告，以便在粉丝介入之前阻止该项目。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，在团队添加了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nightingale-highly-requested-third-person-mode-is-a-big-win-for-fans-3470406">所要求的第三人称模式</a>后，煤气灯奇幻生存游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/nightingale"><em>《Nightingale》</em></a>的粉丝感觉被开发者看到了。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/grand-theft-auto-cluckin-bell-restaurant-issued-a-cease-and-desist-3470443">《侠盗猎车手》Cluckin&#39; Bell 餐厅发出停止令的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
